{"tid":418794,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"電動車同環保有咩關係？？","createTime":"2017-09-30T01:19:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-30T02:07:41.000Z","uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6432478e7a3ed02104d95c2f64419b16e1a8a6a6","tid":418794,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:19:21.000Z","msg":"電動車 ： 用電作為能源 <br />\n<br />\n果d 電, 知唔知係點產生? <br />\n&quot;香港的發電廠以<span style=\"color: red;\">煤作為主要發電的燃料</span>，其次為天然氣。&quot; (by wiki) <br />\n<br />\n而，燃煤會: <br />\n- 釋出硫化物、氮氧化物、及微塵<br />\n- 釋放大量的二氧化碳氣體到外界環境<br />\n- 就含有長半衰期的放射性物質鈾及釷<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n真心唔明電動車環保條撚 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對環境而言，根本就係 屎 vs 屎"},{"pid":"32c0f1d7d51a0ac1efa3b2dcca59d5104d1d51ec","tid":418794,"uid":20213,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:30:49.000Z","msg":"樓主好撚醒 以為得自己知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一 電動車efficiency高過汽油車<br />\n二 少路面污染"},{"pid":"71049900a72f69d0aa32923edbe97a04a04bb3c0","tid":418794,"uid":1518,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:31:35.000Z","msg":"人力車最環保"},{"pid":"3bc82f31cf967ec04c4bf75926fe55009e23918c","tid":418794,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:32:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主好撚醒 以為得自己知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一 電動車efficiency高過汽油車<br />\n二 <span style=\"color: red;\">少路面污染</span></blockquote><br />\n發電廠發電唔會污染？"},{"pid":"eb10565625f0130f8ecb98f58b8d8941f1ec1262","tid":418794,"uid":61748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:33:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"45f7afcb5303c40d485d80039537c3a73124aa90","tid":418794,"uid":20213,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:33:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主好撚醒 以為得自己知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一 電動車efficiency高過汽油車<br />\n二 <span style=\"color: red;\">少路面污染</span></blockquote><br />\n發電廠發電唔會污染？</blockquote><br />\n路面呀 你識唔識字呀？路面多人啲定發電廠區多人啲呀？"},{"pid":"5e01b307ea66e45131ec271738ee4eaee1c854cb","tid":418794,"uid":28151,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:34:54.000Z","msg":"電廠有大型設備集中處理排放物, 處理污染物效果比汽車好<br />\n加埋用電嘅efficiency 比油車高 (starting, regenerative breaking, no idling)<br />\nU嘅時候做過功課, 香港電動車每公里排放量係比汽油車低<br />\n而電廠未來發電燃料比例改善會進一步拉開差距"},{"pid":"753eb9afcd92fe57a99ad9673c6b5ca6ae353d62","tid":418794,"uid":102763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:35:31.000Z","msg":"On9樓主。知唔知每年我地用唔曬d電都唔要<br />\n依家有個方法用盡d唔好？"},{"pid":"1650668907acf08d0b6e41b0f9e40b76a084c67e","tid":418794,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:36:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主好撚醒 以為得自己知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一 電動車efficiency高過汽油車<br />\n二 <span style=\"color: red;\">少路面污染</span></blockquote><br />\n發電廠發電唔會污染？</blockquote><br />\n路面呀 你識唔識字呀？路面多人啲定發電廠區多人啲呀？</blockquote><br />\n發電廠機組發電效率高過車<br />\n就算石油發電都用少啲油"},{"pid":"0348a56e2396321f296b2e48bbf1d8e98f42cee2","tid":418794,"uid":61954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:36:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>電廠有大型設備集中處理排放物, 處理污染物效果比汽車好<br />\n加埋用電嘅efficiency 比油車高 (starting, regenerative breaking, no idling)<br />\nU嘅時候做過功課, 香港電動車每公里排放量係比汽油車低<br />\n而電廠未來發電燃料比例改善會進一步拉開差距</blockquote><br />\n樓主on9㗎<br />\n你點話佢都可以反駁"},{"pid":"09f2a9d1519fb6bf769fe270c8474db941756b01","tid":418794,"uid":127767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-30T01:36:58.000Z","msg":"你條問題問<strong>電動車</strong>同<strong>環保</strong>有咩關係<br />\n<br />\n事實上係<strong>香港仲用媒發電</strong>唔環保<br />\n唔係電動車唔環保<br />\n人地Elon Musk買起SolarCity整PowerWall起Gigafactory<br />\n目的就係要取代石油<br />\n係香港on99固步自封咋"},{"pid":"29dbdd89578a60bf8ce2ed70928965592fa966f4","tid":41879